		{"id":"924c8f4c85a97aa5","type":"text","text":"## Technical Skills and Craft","x":-320,"y":-271,"width":320,"height":111,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1b966c052243316e","type":"text","text":"### **What you are learning and building technically.**\n\nHands-on work with code, systems, tools, architectures, bugs, frameworks, architecture patterns, design trade-offs and design decisions that show how you think as an engineer.","x":-878,"y":-497,"width":478,"height":266,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e517ab76edc174b3","type":"text","text":"### **How you are growing as an IT professional.**\n\nWhat you built, shipped, tried, broke, or debugged—proof that you can apply knowledge and execute, not just study theory.","x":-877,"y":-172,"width":477,"height":213,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"d48fa02b3b7ab8ad","type":"text","text":"### **Who you are becoming, not just what you know.**\n\nCommunication, teamwork, discipline, resilience, ethics, and the inner work that shapes a reliable, trustworthy professional.","x":500,"y":-321,"width":440,"height":201,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"bcb3d50beec335eb","type":"text","text":"## Professional Growth & Industry Awareness","x":62,"y":-215,"width":340,"height":116,"color":"5"},
