		{"id":"58e5d0211b260541","type":"text","text":"### Mindset, values & Philosophy","x":62,"y":-391,"width":340,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b35608d228769cb0","type":"text","text":"### **How you understand the broader tech landscape.**\n\nHow you’re developing as a working professional—teamwork, communication, understanding roles, career navigation, and industry context.","x":500,"y":-85,"width":440,"height":205,"color":"5"},
